{"tid":2508884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國軍艦巡防亞洲路線將避台灣海峽 友台議員痛批如「對中國磕頭」","createTime":"2021-04-29T05:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T06:19:07.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ac4beb657d7b49040bf8f294bb6dd5e2a36880","tid":2508884,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.newtalk.tw/resize_action2/600/album/news/570/6089f6e5ca9ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.newtalk.tw%2Fresize_action2%2F600%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F570%2F6089f6e5ca9ba.jpg&h=d0f82d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國將派軍艦到亞洲，回程時將避開台灣海峽，挨批是向中國「磕頭」。   圖：翻攝德國海軍網頁bundeswehr.de<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-29/569278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-04-29%2F569278&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=9c2f7d3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-29/569278</a><br />\n<br />\n中國近年不斷擴充軍備，軍事行動頻頻，引起國際社會警惕。德國積極投入印太確保航道自由和領土完整，下半年將派軍艦到亞洲，回程時穿越南海，不過，為避免得罪北京，這艘軍艦將避開台灣海峽，引起國會友台議員不滿，痛批此舉是向中國「磕頭」。<br />\n<br />\n根據25日出刊的德國「週日世界報」（Welt Am Sonntag）報導，德國政府認定台灣海峽是國際海域，不過根據國防部的規劃，即將啟程前往亞洲的巡防艦「巴伐利亞」（Bayern）號將不會通過台灣海峽。德艦刻意繞過台海，引起國會友台議員的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n去年9月，德國首度針對印度太平洋地區擬定完整的外交方針，準備積極參與亞洲事務，並規劃今年8月派遣巡防艦到澳洲、朝鮮半島和南海，與澳洲、日本和美國等盟邦進行演習。國防部長康坎鮑爾（Annegret Kramp-Karrenbauer）表示，派艦目的是確保航道自由和領土完整，並向美國釋出訊號。<br />\n<br />\n該報導指出，為了避免得罪北京，德國海軍這艘巡防艦將會避開台灣海峽。對此。德國自民黨（FDP）議員雷希特 （Ulrich Lechte）批評，通過台海象徵對台灣自由和民主的支持；反之，避開則是向中國「磕頭」，德國打算積極投入印太卻又磕頭，實在令人意外。"},{"pid":"5e1c561e7b426ff6fe29a5e60b7f9032691e2008","tid":2508884,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b921c1daaf43bea4243efc20092f2d5d18af2b9","tid":2508884,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"唔好激嬲中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb62e51eef10a26a02d38f6ecedc2ce0d9a12cb","tid":2508884,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b921c1daaf43bea4243efc20092f2d5d18af2b9","tid":2508884,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"唔好激嬲中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"又係因為人民幣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e40a6db477f0afe55d866513176b75263399f56","tid":2508884,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"索性唔嚟"},{"pid":"7174232b689012e90c823deff9e94b282878cde0","tid":2508884,"uid":19640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:00:07.000Z","msg":"堂堂德意志民族為咗人民幣跪低等人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5dca4a917f091900f42216951767a04194145a","tid":2508884,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:03:26.000Z","msg":"派隻1993年落水既古董黎，真係好撚有誠意咁跪"},{"pid":"e512ea288b0f7ad6cb75811f42915191dbd6d9fb","tid":2508884,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50dd7da6d7dbf1dd6cc6be750b0e4a2ff579176","tid":2508884,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ee7d2c9d407de3e02d82b67dee129f8b1b4483","tid":2508884,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"我又唔係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n施壓威嚇就好似鋤D咁，都會留一手，唔會一黎就出大牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}